Class RuleTriple

  • java.lang.Object
    • gr.athenainnovation.imis.fusion.fetcher.rules.RuleTriple

  • public class RuleTriple
extends Object
    Represents an unparsed rule for matching triples against a dataset as it is read from the configuration files.

    Thomas Maroulis
